President Muhammadu Buhari has approved the re-appointment of Dr Samuel Ankeli, as his Senior Special Assistant (SSA) on Disability Matters. The President also re-appointed Shehu Garba as Special Assistant (SA), Disability Matters. A statement by Malam Garba Shehu, Senior Special Assistant to the President (Media & Publicity) said in that “the appointments take effect from October 15, 2019.”